  • READY-TO-GO: Each BN-LINK Wireless Remote Control Outlet kit contains everything you need to start (even the remote batteries!). Simply plug and play, or sync up the outlets to suit your needs.
  • STRONG SIGNAL: Our RF receivers and transmitters work through doors and walls without interfering with other electronics. Signal can function as far as 100 ft in line of sight.
  • FLEXIBILITY: With the option to pair multiple BN-Link remote outlets together, you can expand your system and make the appliances in your home all accessible in just the palm of your hands!
  • SIMPLE CONVENIENCE: Use the remote or the outlets themselves to turn your appliances on and off. Great with almost any electronic device, including lights, air conditioners, heaters, audio sound systems, holiday decorations, and charging devices.
  • SAFE AND RELIABLE: Outlets will remain off after a power outage to save energy and protect your appliances. Ratings: 120V, 10A, 1200W (NOT COMPATIBLE WITH SHOP VACS)

Product description

BN-LINK Remote Control Outlet Switch

(1 Remote + 3 Outlets )

Link your everyday appliances to our handy remote control outlets. Each pack contains everything you'll need to set-up your home, room, or office, including:

  • 1x Remote Control Transmitter, 3x Programmable Outlets
  • 1x 12V/23A Battery, 1x Instruction Manual
  • Ratings 125V, 60Mz, 10A, 1250W

Simply plug and press the buttons. No need for WIFI connection, smartphone, or smarthome device.

Use with your lights, fans, radios, A/C units, and small appliances.

The compact design can be plugged into any standard electrical outlet.

Easily Manage Multiple devices From a Distance

The BN-LINK remote control operates on batteries and can be used from a distance of up to 100 feet away, making it very convenient to use.

Ease of Use for All Ages

The ability to control electrical devices with BN-LINK remote control from a distance can be particularly helpful for older individuals with limited mobility or difficulty reaching electrical outlets.

Save Energy & Money

Reduce power consumption and extends products using life by up to 15%.

100 Feet Wireless Range

Powerful RF signal can find otulets through doors and walls without interfering with WiFi or cell phone frequencies.

One remote, Multiple outlets

Program multiple remotes with one outlet to allow the entire family to control a frequently used device

Make Your Life Easier

With a touch of a button, you can start a fan, turn off a bedside lamp.
